WEBVTT

00:00:00.150 --> 00:00:01.980
Welcome to my website,

00:00:01.980 --> 00:00:03.270
Kleiderordnung Berlin.

00:00:03.300 --> 00:00:05.310
I'm Tina, the founder,

00:00:05.310 --> 00:00:09.330
and I work as a stylist with
a focus on sustainability.

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:18.030
You can't book wild shopping trips
with me,

00:00:18.030 --> 00:00:21.000
but we'll start together
at your wardrobe

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:22.680
with my
Wardrobe Deep Dive,

00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:24.270
because there's nothing
more sustainable

00:00:24.270 --> 00:00:27.090
than getting creative with
what you already own.

00:00:30.690 --> 00:00:34.290
Thanks to my
enthusiasm for second-hand,

00:00:34.290 --> 00:00:36.810
vintage, and flea market pieces,

00:00:36.990 --> 00:00:39.420
I was lucky enough to
discover my talent

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:41.700
for getting creative with

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.340
a wide variety of pieces and
putting a consistent look

00:00:44.340 --> 00:00:45.420
together.

00:00:50.310 --> 00:00:51.870
If you think: "wow,
I need Tina

00:00:51.870 --> 00:00:55.050
by my side",
but you're concerned

00:00:55.050 --> 00:00:57.000
"Oh, am I prepared well enough?
Do I already have

00:00:57.888 --> 00:01:00.840
a clear vision?
Do I know all about trends?

00:01:01.140 --> 00:01:03.420
Does the scale show what
I was hoping for?"

00:01:03.420 --> 00:01:05.069
then I can ease your worries.

00:01:05.069 --> 00:01:07.230
Just come as you are,

00:01:07.230 --> 00:01:09.000
as you are in your life
right now.

00:01:09.030 --> 00:01:11.500
I am very much looking forward
to meeting you.

00:01:13.200 --> 00:01:16.230
If you're really keen
on something new,

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:18.960
that work well with
what you already own

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:20.610
then we'll be happy to look for

00:01:20.610 --> 00:01:23.730
second-hand alternatives or visit

00:01:23.730 --> 00:01:25.860
a high-quality vintage boutique or a
fair fashion store like this one together.

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:30.330
If you think this is exactly right for you,

00:01:30.330 --> 00:01:32.730
I look forward to getting to know you!
